{"tid":1389621,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"沈旭暉：如何理解政治中立","createTime":"2019-07-31T02:49:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T03:01:07.000Z","uid":278231,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f53547fc7b7c1b7018255cde9e3684b264372a89","tid":1389621,"uid":278231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:49:16.000Z","msg":"AO朋友傳來今天SCMP一篇文章，大概是英文的關係，不會有太多人看，但他們認為很值得警惕。這篇讀者來信認為，&ldquo;the government should make sure the AOs selected during future recruitment exercises are absolutely devoted to the government&rdquo;，也就是公然的政治審查，而且工作期間必須有&rdquo;absolute neutrality&quot;，也就是對上級無條件服從。<br />\n<br />\n朋友笑說，they'd better hire a robot, or have you converted into one。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，如何理解「政治中立」，是文明衝突的重要內容。我們接受的教育一直鼓吹獨立思考，反對非黑即白，相信獨立思考的人在不同崗位，都能達到社會最大效益。文官制度在「政治正確」觀念下逐漸敗壞，變成一群沒有核心價值、只懂得舞文弄墨的技術官僚主導，提倡盲目服從更高層政治任務的「新常態」，假如這次沒有那百多位AO表態，整個制度的腐化，只會更全速推行。希望大家多用自己的方式，支持在不同崗位的有心人，這才是香港精神。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/223783954322429/posts/2615424258491708?s=669503810&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F223783954322429%2Fposts%2F2615424258491708%3Fs%3D669503810%26sfns%3Dmo&d=z0v15oAQEaIuorZt047Ij5LurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=62f3d628\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/223783954322429/posts/2615424258491708?s=669503810&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"62afbf42e40f1456d4edd0d7158f61e400e169ac","tid":1389621,"uid":278231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:51:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c0648c7c923a3889832ab839aab18e48951fc808","tid":1389621,"uid":4574,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:58:08.000Z","msg":"政治中立係笑話<br />\n<br />\n大是大非上<br />\n無得唔表態<br />\n<br />\n八國聯軍、日本仔打中國<br />\n有無得政治中立？<br />\n如果有<br />\n汪精衛就唔會死 <br />\n仲落得漢奸污名<br />\n<br />\n呢啲政治中立撚<br />\n仲可怕過納粹、法西斯主義者 <br />\n蘇維埃毒瘤"},{"pid":"80d0a0c3cdfe48967b19380570462d09d9555fdd","tid":1389621,"uid":68822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:01:07.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ErY1NGl2p_M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DErY1NGl2p_M&d=z0v15oAQEaIuorZt047Ij5LurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=e276e7d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ErY1NGl2p_M</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwGX_Vgq-1G0&d=z0v15oAQEaIuorZt047Ij5LurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=b25b571b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0</a><br />\n</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港！時代革命！<br />\nLiberate Hong Kong! <br />\nThe Revolution Of Our Times! </span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>五大訴求</strong></span></span></ins><br />\n 1. 徹底撤回逃犯修訂條例<br />\n 2. 釋放所有因反送中被捕人士並承諾永不追究<br />\n 3. 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n 4. 追究警察濫權濫暴(包括721元朗官警黑勾結事件)，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n 5. 立即實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins>Hongkongers 5 Demands:</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n1. Full Withdrawal of the Extradition Bill<br />\n2. Retraction of the Characterisation of the Protestas a Riot<br />\n3. Release all Arrested Protesters<br />\n4. Accountability for Police and Yuen Long White Shirts Brutality<br />\n5. Implement Dual Universal Suffrage<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/Rcba2Hh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRcba2Hh.png&h=a61a5d44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/fm6yf2o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffm6yf2o.jpg&h=67e4b0d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時間無多，政府拖字訣，想我地自亂陣腳，行動規模必須升級</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}